<ArticleLayout
  title="Courts Are Now Pricing the Generation Gap"
  description="AI hallucinations are no longer theoretical. In Q1 2026 alone, U.S. courts sanctioned attorneys for more than $145,000 in AI-generated legal hallucinations. The Generation Gap is being priced."
  canonical="/insights/courts-pricing-the-generation-gap"
